ings\" title=\"Statue Of Blessings\">Statue Of Blessings</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_The_Dwarf_King\" title=\"Statue Of The Dwarf King\">Statue Of The Dwarf King</a> •  <a href=\"/Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\">Telephone</a> • <a href=\"/Tent_Kit\" title=\"Tent Kit\">Tent Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a> • <a href=\"/Workbench\" title=\"Workbench\">Workbench</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414051817\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.111 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.124 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 8077/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10739/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1740/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2794/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   86.808      1 -total\n 51.74%   44.912      1 Template:Infobox\n 49.78%   43.212      4 Template:Description\n 16.21%   14.071      3 Template:Name\n  5.79%    5.022      3 Template:Duration\n  4.70%    4.084      1 Template:Health\n  4.53%    3.935      1 Template:Energy\n  3.63%    3.154      7 Template:Price\n  2.39%    2.078      1 Template:History\n  1.52%    1.316      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:15017-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414051817 and revision id 182089\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Dehydrator\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = [[Pierre's]] for {{Price|10000}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Wood|30}}{{Name|Clay|2}}{{Name|Fire Quartz|1}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Dehydrator''' is a type of [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]] that is used to create raisins and dried mushrooms and fruit. It can be crafted after purchasing the recipe from [[Pierre]] for {{Price|10000}}. It is also a possible reward as the 12th prize from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]] in the Mayor's Manor (50% chance). One is included if the player chooses the [[The Cave#Mushrooms|mushroom cave]].\n\n==Products==\nDehydrator requires five [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushrooms]] (except [[Red Mushroom]]) or [[Fruits]] of the same '''type''' and '''quality'''.\n<section begin=\"dehydratorproducts\"/><!--Transcluded onto Artisan Goods page-->\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredients\n!Processing Time\n!Sell Price\n!Energy / Health\n|-\n||[[File:Dried Mushrooms.png|center]]\n|[[Dried Mushrooms]]\n|{{Description|Dried Mushrooms}}\n|5 of Any [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushroom]] (except [[Red Mushroom]])\n|data-sort-value=\"01\"|{{Duration|1 day|class=inline}} (ready the next morning)\n|7.5 &times; [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushroom]] Base Price + {{Price|25}} (1.5 &times; Base + {{Price|5}} per [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushroom]])\n|3 &times; base [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushroom]] Energy/Health restoration\n|-\n||[[File:Dried Fruit.png|center]]\n|[[Dried Fruit]]\n|{{Description|Dried Fruit}}\n|5 of Any [[Fruits|Fruit]] (except [[Grape]]s)\n|data-sort-value=\"01\"|{{Duration|1 day|class=inline}} (ready the next morning)\n|7.5 &times; [[Fruits|Fruit]] Base Price + {{Price|25}} (1.5 &times; Base + {{Price|5}} per [[Fruits|Fruit]])\n|3 &times; base [[Fruits]] Energy/Health restoration\n|-\n||[[File:Raisins.png|center]]\n|[[Raisins]]\n|{{Description|Raisins}}\n|5 [[Grape]]s\n|data-sort-value=\"01\"|{{Duration|1 day|class=inline}} (ready the next morning)\n|{{Price|600}}\n|{{energy|125}}{{health|56}}\n|}<section end=\"dehydratorproducts\"/>\n\n==Notes==\n* The quality of the dried product is always normal and '''not''' affected by the quality of items used.\n* Inedible fruits become edible after being turned into [[Dried Fruit]]. The formula for [[Energy]] is: <samp>[Base fruit sell price ÷ 2 × 0.5 × 5]</samp>, or <samp>[Base fruit sell price × 1.25]</samp>. ''This is the same as the calculation for base silver quality sell price, but rounded instead of truncated.''\n**Dried [[Ancient Fruit]]s give 688 [[Energy]] and 309 [[Health]]\n**Dried [[Coconut]]s give 125 [[Energy]] and 56 [[Health]]\n**Dried [[Rhubarb]]s give 275 [[Energy]] and 123 [[Health]]\n* The dehydrator effectively makes the [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushrooms]] or [[Fruits]] sell at gold quality price +5 each.\n* [[Truffle]]s are not classified as [[:Category:Mushrooms|mushrooms]] and therefore cannot be placed into the Dehydrator.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.6|Introduced.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Dehydrator]]\n[[es:Deshidratador]]\n[[fr:Déshydrateur]]\n[[it:Essiccatore]]\n[[ja:乾燥器]]\n[[ko:탈수기]]\n[[hu:Aszaló]]\n[[pt:Desidratador]]\n[[ru:Сушилка]]\n[[tr:Kurutucu]]\n[[zh:烘干机]]"
    }
